OL,3,CYouths appear in court charged over
OL,4,CEly riots in Cardiff
OL,6,FA further five adults and eight youths
OL,7,Fhave appeared in court charged with
OL,8,Foffences related to a riot which
OL,9,Ffollowed the deaths of two teenagers
OL,10,Fin a crash in Cardiff last year.
OL,12,FTensions in the Ely area of the city
OL,13,Fboiled over following the deaths of
OL,14,FKyrees Sullivan, 16, and Harvey Evans,
OL,15,F15, on the evening of May 22, 2023,
OL,16,Fwhen they crashed on an e-bike minutes
OL,17,Fafter CCTV captured them being
OL,18,Ffollowed by a South Wales Police van.
