OL,3,CYouths appear in court charged over
OL,4,CEly riots in Cardiff
OL,6,FLocal people and police at the scene
OL,7,Fclashed, leading to a riot which
OL,8,Flasted several hours, during which
OL,9,Ftime dozens of officers were injured,
OL,10,Fproperty was damaged and cars were set
OL,11,Falight.
OL,13,FThe 13 adults and youths appeared
OL,14,Fbefore Cardiff Magistrates' Court on
OL,15,FFriday, 20 September, charged with
OL,16,Foffences related to the event.
