OL,3,CYouths appear in court charged over
OL,4,CEly riots in Cardiff
OL,6,FThe adults appearing were Lee
OL,7,FRobinson, 37, from Cardiff, charged
OL,8,Fwith riot; Janine Reffell, 53, from
OL,9,FEly, Cardiff, charged with criminal
OL,10,Fdamage; Morgan Williams, 18, from
OL,11,FPentwyn, Cardiff, charged with
OL,12,Fthreatening to cause criminal damage;
OL,13,FJayden Williams, 18, from Grangetown,
OL,14,FCardiff, charged with threatening to
OL,15,Fcause criminal damage, and McKenzie
OL,16,FPring, 19, who appeared by video-link
OL,17,Ffrom HMP Parc, charged with riot.
OL,19,FThe youths, who cannot be named for
OL,20,Flegal reasons, are aged between 15 and
OL,21,F17.
