OL,3,CYouths appear in court charged over
OL,4,CEly riots in Cardiff
OL,6,FSeven of the youths were charged with
OL,7,Friot, to which they all pleaded not
OL,8,Fguilty.
OL,10,FOne was charged with threatening to
OL,11,Fcause criminal damage, and pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty.
OL,14,FBelinda Sullivan and Nadine Evans, the
OL,15,Fmothers of Kyrees Sullivan and Harvey
OL,16,FEvans, were in court for Friday's
OL,17,Fhearing.
OL,19,FDistrict Judge Stephen Harmes set a
OL,20,Ftrial for December 16 listed for five
OL,21,Fdays for the youths.
