OL,3,CYouths appear in court charged over
OL,4,CEly riots in Cardiff
OL,6,FAll the defendants were granted
OL,7,Funconditional bail except Pring, who
OL,8,Fremains at HMP Parc.
OL,10,FReffell and twins Morgan and Jayden
OL,11,FWilliams pleaded guilty to their
OL,12,Foffences, the rest did not enter pleas.
OL,14,FDistrict Judge Stephen Harmes told the
OL,15,Fcourt Reffell had pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fdamaging a Peugeot 308 police vehicle,
OL,17,Fcausing less than #5,000 of damage.
OL,19,FShe will next appear before the court
OL,20,Fon November 26 for sentencing.
