OL,3,CYouths appear in court charged over
OL,4,CEly riots in Cardiff
OL,6,FHe said: "You caused criminal damage
OL,7,Fto the rear window on the day of the
OL,8,Friots on an adjoining street away from
OL,9,Fthe rest of the rioting."
OL,11,FTwins Morgan and Jayden Williams, both
OL,12,F18, pleaded guilty to threatening to
OL,13,Fcause criminal damage.
OL,15,FThe court heard that one of the twins
OL,16,Fsaid: "Your station, your police
OL,17,Fstation is getting blown up tonight.
OL,18,FThat's on my brother's grave."
